    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK533">
<l>poccāppārk killai pukaḻmai yatulakat</l>
<l>teppāṉū lōrkkun tuṇivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Thoughtlessness will never acquire fame and this tenet is upheld by all treatises in the world.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
